Asynchronized Grep For Vim

Install(unix):

    # cd ~/.vim/bundle
    # git clone https://github.com/mattn/asyncgrep-vim.git
    # git clone https://github.com/ynkdir/vim-remote.git
    # cd vim-remote/src
    # make -f Makefile.x11
    # cp vimremote ~/.vim/bundle/asyncgrep-vim/script/.

Install(windows):

    # cd %USERPROFILE%/vimfiles/bundle
    # git clone https://github.com/mattn/asyncgrep-vim.git
    # git clone https://github.com/ynkdir/vim-remote.git
    # cd vim-remote/src
    # mingw32-make -f Makefile.mingw (or nmake -f Makefile.msvc)
    # copy vimremote.exe ..\..\asyncgrep-vim\script

Usage:

    :Agrep foo
    :Agrep foo **/*.c

Author:

    asyncgrep-vim: Yasuhiro Matsumoto
    vim-remote:    Yukihiro Nakadaira

